Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:44.23,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Customers will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:47.74,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Can we get this over with?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.02,0:01:48.87,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Customers?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:50.50,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Ha! Nobody's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.26,0:01:54.18,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Nobody wants to eat at this shit hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.22,0:01:56.20,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.43,0:01:58.97,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Everybody needs to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:02.30,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, do you have my money?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.28,0:02:05.25,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,You better not be a single yen short.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.42,0:02:08.64,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,If you don't have it all,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.68,0:02:11.16,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,know that you can't run away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.26,0:02:15.77,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I'll ruin your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.67,0:02:21.89,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Fifty million yen, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.67,0:02:21.89,NLE - Notes,,0,0,0,,${\a6}43,9887 USD
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:42.55,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Too bad, huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:45.52,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,What'd you expect, lending to the poor?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:53.22,NLE - Title,,0,0,0,,{\fscx118\fscy200\pos(322.289,339.857)}The Restaurant of Murderous Intent
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:57.62,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I'll hide her here for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:03:02.26,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I'll move her to the mountains at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:09.96,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,You deserve this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:13.36,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Who has fifty million yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:14.85,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Look at this fucking place...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:18.43,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,A shitty guitar and an old record player.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:21.10,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,All this country music shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:23.83,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,It's not even popular here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.83,0:03:25.68,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,No wonder she needed her money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:29.20,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Gah! There're rats here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:30.19,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:31.20,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:34.34,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Let's take a break and grab a cup of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:36.53,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Good idea. Let's stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:39.40,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I dunno about this place. Looks closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:42.09,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,But the sign says they're open.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.29,0:03:43.39,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:46.86,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Shit! If they come in now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:54.44,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that place over there looks nicer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:56.72,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,You're right. Wanna go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:04.98,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Ah, that one's closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:08.06,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,That's it then. We'll get our coffee here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:10.98,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Really? This place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:15.76,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Hi! How's it goin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:18.74,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Oh, something smells good here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:21.44,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:24.62,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Please, seat yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:27.97,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,This place is actually pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:34.40,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:36.40,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,What're you doing, Kindaichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:37.49,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,My bad, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:40.56,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for that scare, master.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:42.01,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:44.44,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,As long as you're not hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:47.57,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Master, are you the only one here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:49.24,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.46,0:04:51.10,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I can't afford anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.51,0:04:54.53,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Hey, old man. Do you smell something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:57.04,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:59.93,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I think I can smell some blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:05.34,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,No, actually, until now I was preparing a bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:07.98,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,The scent of blood's still lingering in the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:10.70,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Ah, so you're cooking a bird right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:12.34,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.19,0:05:14.24,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Lemme see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:20.15,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,T-This meat--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:21.91,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,0:05:22.64,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Is it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.33,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,H-He knows!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.08,0:05:27.40,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Rib roast?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:28.55,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:30.20,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,That's high quality beef!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:34.84,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,It sure is tasty...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.45,0:05:38.31,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,And it smells so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:40.79,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,What's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:42.90,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,This reminds me of a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:46.62,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,This guy used frozen meat as a murder weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:47.68,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:52.49,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Then he tried to cook it and feed it to the detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:55.78,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,That's right. What an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:58.28,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Just who are these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.08,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to order?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:03.20,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.41,0:06:06.56,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,We'll take two cups of the house blend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.56,0:06:08.42,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I bet it's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:11.25,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I have a good feeling about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:12.74,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:18.68,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, master?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:22.17,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,A-Ah, yes. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:29.84,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I've only ever made instant coffee before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.97,0:06:33.60,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Am I supposed to put the coffee powder in the tea strainer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:35.34,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:41.62,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,That's got to be too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:48.42,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,It's so dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:49.71,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:53.57,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,If I give them some shitty coffee, maybe they'll leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:56.14,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.41,0:06:59.50,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,It smells really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:00.10,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:01.60,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,No need for milk or sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:02.81,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Very funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:09.66,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,No good? It's not like anyone could drink that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:12.49,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,That's right. Hurry up and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:12.49,NLE - Yellow,,0,0,0,,Old man? You alright? Old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:15.38,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:19.22,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,This is the true taste of bitterness!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.30,0:07:22.69,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Way too freakin' bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:24.69,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Hey, does he have no taste buds?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:28.38,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,How could he drink that without dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:31.08,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,What's with these two?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:34.14,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,What a strange pairing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.52,0:07:38.22,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,They don't seem like family, or student and teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:40.77,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Brothers? Couldn't be... friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.07,0:07:45.36,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Yes, Division One, Inspector Kenmochi here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.07,0:07:45.36,NLE - Notes,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Division One = Homicide
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:47.82,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:50.28,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,And he's the one in charge of homicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:52.90,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,What? A woman was murdered?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:55.64,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,He's got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:57.33,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,You already made the arrest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:59.64,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,And you already have a full confession?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:02.63,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,There was a threat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:04.08,NLE - Yellow,,0,0,0,,It's not about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:08.26,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Looks like my day off's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:09.48,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,No worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:11.99,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,But I'm starting to get hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:13.99,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna eat something here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:15.42,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:18.36,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,The coffee was so good, we should grab lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:20.63,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Master! Menu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:24.06,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Why the hell won't they leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:30.43,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Alright! I'll have the special sautéed bird and rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.87,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Ah, actually, that's--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.87,0:08:35.86,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,What? Weren't you preparing bird earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:38.28,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,That's for someone with a dinner reservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:41.92,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I can only make you beef or curry right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:43.67,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Then I'll have the curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.67,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I'll take the sautéed beef!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:47.23,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Coming right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.39,0:08:52.62,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Curry and beef... they're getting all the spices!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.96,0:08:56.20,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Hey, master!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:56.80,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Yes...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.02,0:08:58.31,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Where's the toilet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:00.63,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,T-The t-toilet is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:04.30,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Aha, there it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:06.54,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Please me more careful when you stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:10.23,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,That was a close one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:12.57,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Hey, master?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:13.86,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Yes, what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:15.26,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,There's no TP.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:18.23,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.23,0:09:19.70,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Eh! Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:20.68,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,So sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:21.99,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:29.34,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Check it out! They're actually stacked to the ceiling in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:31.83,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,You should remember this sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:33.62,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.33,0:09:38.28,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,What was he planning to do without toilet paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:41.50,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Hello, is anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:44.04,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,It's Ishihara, the cleaner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.19,0:09:46.66,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I've finished laundering your uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.66,0:09:48.25,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Ah, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:50.14,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,That's your uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:54.44,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I knew you wouldn't cook in a shirt like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:55.82,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Lucky it didn't get dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:59.28,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's a good thing it's arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:02.54,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's better!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:03.06,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:04.75,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:09.48,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,So you're like this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:14.69,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,How is it? Looks good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:20.49,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I-I've no choice but to endure this humiliation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.84,0:10:26.48,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:28.91,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,So much curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:31.00,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,But there's not much meat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:34.85,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Superb! This is the perfect blend of spices.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:37.28,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Master, you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:44.33,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,It really is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:46.55,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Hey old man, we should get dessert too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:47.82,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:52.99,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Master, can we get the cold watermelon and petal cookies? Oh, and more coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.22,0:10:55.18,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Coming right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:57.67,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,They're ordering more...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:00.99,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:02.62,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,It was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:05.07,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I hope the dessert's as good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:06.82,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:23.96,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Just what's with these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:26.60,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,That's a lot of records.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:28.08,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Think they're all country?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.28,0:11:31.70,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,How nostalgic. Reminds me of the good ol' days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:34.92,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Hey, master!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:39.99,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,It says on here that you'll play requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:41.46,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I'm requesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:43.89,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,You want me to play the guitar?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:47.40,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Why'd that woman have something so unnecessary!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:48.74,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Hold it, Kindaichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:52.26,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I chose this place, so I get the first request!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.26,0:11:55.08,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Eh? But I already asked!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:55.61,NLE - Yellow,,0,0,0,,No, it's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:57.97,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I can't play any instruments!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:01.82,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I'm never gonna get outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:05.36,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Ouch, ouch, ouch, ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:06.96,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, master?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:08.56,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I cut my finger on the broken dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:11.33,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I can't play the guitar now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.49,0:12:12.74,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:16.06,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Master, we should treat that immediately. Where's your first aid box?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:18.14,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, it's not that bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.14,0:12:21.09,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,For this kind of injury, cellophane tape is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:22.86,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:26.35,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Really? I've never heard of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:29.27,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,It's true. I saw it on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:12:58.62,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:04.32,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Why's the bench filled with these?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:07.42,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,That's actually where I store my vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:16.09,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Geez, when you yelled like that, I thought something else was gonna come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.09,0:13:17.40,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:18.90,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Like maybe a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:21.82,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Very funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:24.91,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Well, then, here's the watermelon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:30.04,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Here's your watermelon and petal cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:31.92,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:34.79,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,These petal cookies are great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.97,0:13:37.30,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,It was a long battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:39.73,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,You can't buy anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:41.73,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:46.64,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,This watermelon is so cold. It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:14:00.90,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I'm so full. It's about time we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.35,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Master, check please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.35,0:14:03.14,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:05.08,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,That'll be ¥2,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:05.08,NLE - Notes,,0,0,0,,{\a6}¥2,000 = $17.62 US
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:07.03,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,¥2,000? Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:09.60,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,That's not enough for this level of service.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:11.24,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,No, it's really alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:13.74,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I just ask that you come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:16.14,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:20.60,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,We were pretty lucky today to have found this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:21.56,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:24.66,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Just a sec, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:26.96,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you forget something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:28.45,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I forgot something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:32.21,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I've got my cell, wallet, and police notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.01,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,What did I forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:36.70,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,You forgot...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:39.64,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,to investigate the murder here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:40.99,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:44.80,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,And I've already solved the mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:47.44,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,You're not really this shop's master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:49.96,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kindaichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:53.09,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,You had a dispute with the real master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:55.58,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,That was right before we arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:15:00.11,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,You had no choice but to pretend to be the master.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:00.99,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:05.51,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, the victim is hidden somewhere in the shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:13.48,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,The real master is probably a woman, considering that frilly apron.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:17.79,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,The master, rather mama-san, is quite short.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:19.60,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Probably about 155cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:19.60,NLE - Notes,,0,0,0,,{\a6}155cm = 5'1"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:22.55,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,And this place is so messy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:24.23,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,So what if it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:26.91,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,That exposed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.37,0:15:31.26,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,For instance, when you ran into that stepladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:35.62,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,You're pretty tall. Only short people need a stepladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:39.82,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,That stepladder would only be used by mama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:45.66,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,That stepladder isn't the only evidence that you aren't the master.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.22,0:15:49.76,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,You didn't know where the toilet paper was.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:54.47,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,To avoid playing the guitar, you hurt your finger on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:55.35,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:15:57.84,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,the knife and fork!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:03.76,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,When you set the table, you put the knife on the left and fork on the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:05.78,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,S-so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:08.96,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,The knife and fork should be switched.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:12.13,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,You know, I thought something was off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:12.78,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:16.01,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I'm certain they're reversed. Miyuki told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:20.60,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,A real restaurant master wouldn't make such a basic mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:23.00,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.32,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:26.33,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I really am the master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:28.87,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Just where is this imaginary mama-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.43,0:16:32.05,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,You already told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:35.48,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,You gave the hint while cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:40.47,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,The watermelon you served for dessert was in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:43.35,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Looking at it got me thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:46.70,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,The menu said it was cold watermelon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:49.28,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,It would be strange if it was cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:52.64,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,And it {\i1}was{\i0} when it was served.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:54.25,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:56.75,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,There can only be one explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:17:00.70,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Until recently, that watermelon must've been in the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:06.10,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Not just the watermelon, but all the vegetables in this bench.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:08.95,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,They're cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:14.66,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,You were nervous when I almost knocked over this bench.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:18.55,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,That's because you filled it with the contents of the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:23.68,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,In other words, you swapped the contents of the fridge and the bench.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:27.53,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Then inside the fridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:37.18,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,The victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:46.64,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Hello! Delivery!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:52.07,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:01.01,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Nice one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:03.18,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I've got a black belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:10.12,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Old man! She's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:10.76,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:11.87,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:12.46,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:15.86,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Hello? This is inspector--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:28.39,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,By the way, when'd you start suspecting that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:30.91,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,When he hit the stepladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.91,0:18:31.49,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.49,0:18:35.60,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,And I was convinced by the calendar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:36.58,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,The calendar?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:39.10,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:41.81,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I knew something was up when I saw the calendar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:45.19,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Hey old man, can't you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:48.19,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I have no clue...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:50.53,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,It's just a calendar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.53,0:18:51.05,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:53.88,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,See how the holidays are marked with flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:57.25,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,The 15th is Respect the Aged Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:57.25,NLE - Notes,,0,0,0,,{\a6}It's on the 3rd monday in September since 2003.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:18:59.78,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,The 23rd is Autumnal Equinox Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:04.28,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,But there is no holiday on September 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:06.70,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,So why is it marked?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:09.06,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Is there any reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.53,0:19:13.94,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,When mama-san was attacked, she was probably cutting cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:15.19,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Cookies?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:17.98,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,My mom does the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.44,0:19:22.15,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,You knead the flour and sugar,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.15,0:19:25.68,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,then you cut out the shapes and bake them in the oven.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.90,0:19:28.98,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,But if you do it right on the cutting board,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:30.98,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,it'll get stuck and won't really work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:34.05,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,So first you need to put down paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:38.98,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,That mama-san used this calendar for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.10,0:19:43.25,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that kinda gross?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:46.12,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,It's fine if they're for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.47,0:19:49.94,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,She was attacked while making cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:53.11,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,When mama-san was struck, she collapsed onto the counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:56.21,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,That's how this hint came to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:20:00.85,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Because of the flower shape of the cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:06.09,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Mama-san's blood then passed through the hole, staining the calendar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:11.55,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,And the result was this red flower mark on September 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:16.06,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Earlier, I saved one of these cookies to try and match it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:20.50,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,See, a perfect fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:26.49,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,What're the odds the bloodstain would be in the perfect spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:29.55,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,With this hint, I knew there was a case here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:34.89,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,And, the reason why he had to hang up the calendar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.12,0:20:40.60,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,More blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.94,0:20:45.46,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you can't--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:46.50,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Who cares!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.11,0:20:49.89,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,That guy didn't know what this was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.34,0:20:53.31,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Mama-san had taken down the calendar,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:56.69,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,because she was planning to replace it with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:20:58.18,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:01.48,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,She was just gonna use the calendar as parchment paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:05.68,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Hold on! Where's the weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:08.32,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Ah, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:12.05,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,how to put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:16.46,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:17.46,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,You did...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.72,0:21:19.92,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,That fucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:22.75,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,I'll flip that asshole another two or three times!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.75,0:21:24.32,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Hi, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:26.84,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Did you solve the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.96,0:21:28.58,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Hajime-chan, good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.58,0:21:31.51,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,It's thanks to the old man for treating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:34.20,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Apparently he was an assistant professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:38.85,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,He wanted to marry a company president's daughter, but he had troubles with mama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.85,0:21:40.85,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,So how'd you end up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:42.76,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,It's the usual story.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.76,0:21:46.07,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,We were looking for elite coffee, but this place stunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:48.07,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Huh? The coffee was fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.40,0:21:49.25,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.42,0:21:53.86,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,That reminds me! There's a nearby shop that's known for it's really delicious coffee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.86,0:21:54.92,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,You stop there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.05,0:21:57.64,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Did you know that, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:21:58.97,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.12,0:22:02.06,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Time to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.43,0:22:03.16,NLE - Yellow,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:06.54,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Wait up! Where're you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.54,0:22:09.54,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.54,0:22:10.98,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.09,0:23:54.18,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,While camping in a deserted forest, we wandered into a shady laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.95,0:23:59.46,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,There we met some strange med students and mysterious old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.18,0:24:02.20,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,They're looking for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.60,0:24:06.47,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,And in the basement I found traces of something strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.83,0:24:09.36,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,It was the nameplate for Cerberus!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.63,0:24:10.37,NLE - Blue,,0,0,0,,Could it be?
